Prosecutors told jurors that Kevin Knoefel wanted his wife out of the picture but was afraid he'd lose custody of their three-year-old daughter if they divorced. 

During the trial, Zunich said she had fallen in love with her foster father and feared he would commit suicide if she didn't carry out their plot to kill his wife. 

She said it was he who devised the plan to murder his wife.

